SPECTRUM : Spectral Analysis in Python
==========================================

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/spectrum.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/spectrum

.. image:: https://secure.travis-ci.org/cokelaer/spectrum.png
